---
layout: page.njk
title: Planning Commission
subtitle: Reviews development applications, zoning amendments, and land use decisions for Aberdeen.
description: Aberdeen Planning Commission — zoning amendments, subdivision reviews, and land use recommendations.
breadcrumb:
  - label: Boards
    url: /boards/
  - label: Planning Commission
---

<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
  <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-8">

    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">The Planning Commission is a citizen advisory board appointed by the Mayor and City Council. It reviews and makes recommendations on subdivision plans, rezoning requests, special exceptions, and amendments to the City's Comprehensive Plan.</p>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Responsibilities</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-2">
        {% for item in ["Review subdivision plats and site plans", "Make recommendations on rezoning requests", "Hear and decide special exception applications", "Review and update the Comprehensive Plan", "Advise on land use policy and zoning code amendments", "Review Historic District applications"] %}
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
          <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-5 h-5 text-gov-blue flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
          {{ item }}
        </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Upcoming Meeting</h2>
      {% for meeting in events.meetings %}
      {% if "Planning" in meeting.title %}
      <a href="{{ meeting.url }}" class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-4 hover:border-gov-blue transition-all duration-200 group">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-navy text-white rounded-lg flex flex-col items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-center leading-none">
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold opacity-70 uppercase">{{ meeting.month }}</span>
          <span class="text-2xl font-bold">{{ meeting.day }}</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-sm font-bold text-navy group-hover:text-gov-blue transition-colors duration-200">{{ meeting.title }}</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">{{ meeting.location }}</div>
        </div>
      </a>
      {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
      <div class="mt-3"><a href="{{ '/services/meetings/' | url }}" class="text-sm text-gov-blue font-semibold hover:underline">All public meeting agendas →</a></div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">How to Appear Before the Commission</h2>
      <div class="bg-gov-blue-light rounded-xl p-5 text-sm text-slate-700">
        <p class="mb-3">Applications for rezoning, special exceptions, and variances must be submitted to the Planning & Community Development Department before the application deadline.</p>
        <a href="{{ '/departments/planning/' | url }}" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-gov-blue text-white font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-gov-blue-dark transition-colors duration-200 text-sm">Planning Department Info</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <aside>
    <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-6 sticky top-24 space-y-5">
      <h2 class="text-base font-bold text-navy pb-3 border-b border-slate-100">Contact</h2>
      <dl class="space-y-3 text-sm">
        <div><dt class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Staff Contact</dt><dd class="text-slate-700">Planning &amp; Community Development</dd></div>
        <div><dt class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Phone</dt><dd><a href="tel:+14102721600" class="text-gov-blue hover:underline">(410) 272-1600 ext. 221</a></dd></div>
        <div><dt class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Meetings</dt><dd class="text-slate-700">Monthly — Council Chambers<br/>City Hall, 60 N. Parke St.</dd></div>
      </dl>
      <div class="pt-2 space-y-2">
        <a href="{{ '/departments/planning/' | url }}" class="block w-full text-center bg-gov-blue text-white text-sm font-semibold py-2.5 rounded hover:bg-gov-blue-dark transition-colors duration-200">Planning Department</a>
        <a href="{{ '/services/permits/' | url }}" class="block w-full text-center border border-slate-200 text-slate-700 text-sm font-semibold py-2.5 rounded hover:border-gov-blue hover:text-gov-blue transition-colors duration-200">Permits &amp; Applications</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </aside>
</div>
